PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1775139065
OL,3,CRare giant anteater pup born at zoo
OL,5,FA zoo is celebrating a significant
OL,6,Fconservation success following the
OL,7,Fbirth of a rare giant anteater pup.
OL,9,FThe tiny arrival was born at Blackpool
OL,10,FZoo on Monday, 2 March, to 15-year-old
OL,11,Fparents Andina and Eskil.
OL,13,FIt is the fourth baby the pair have
OL,14,Fwelcomed together, and visitors are
OL,15,Falready being treated to the sight of
OL,16,Fthe "tiny" youngster hitching a ride
OL,17,Fon its mum's back.
OL,19,FThe new pup joins a growing household
OL,20,Fthat includes its two-year-old sister,
OL,21,FMyrtle.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
