FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1775139065
OL,3,CRare giant anteater pup born at zoo
OL,5,FWhile the family is expanding locally,
OL,6,Ftwo of Andina and Eskil's older
OL,7,Foffspring have recently moved to join
OL,8,Fother zoo groups across Europe to
OL,9,Fsupport wider breeding programmes.
OL,11,FDespite the "giant" in their name, the
OL,12,Fnew arrival currently measures just
OL,13,F50cm long.
OL,15,FKeepers say they have not determined
OL,16,Fthe pup's gender, as they are allowing
OL,17,FAndina to rear the baby naturally
OL,18,Fwithout interference.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
