FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1775139065
OL,3,CRare giant anteater pup born at zoo
OL,5,FGiant anteaters are known for their
OL,6,Fstriking appearance, featuring black
OL,7,Fand white diagonal stripes, shaggy
OL,8,Fhair, and magnificent bushy tails.
OL,9,FHowever, the baby's distinctive
OL,10,Fmarkings serve a clever purpose.
OL,12,FJason Keller, Senior Keeper, explained
OL,13,Fthat the pup's camouflage makes it a
OL,14,Fchallenge for the untrained eye.
OL,16,FHe said: "The new arrival is already
OL,17,Fable to walk around on its own but,
OL,18,Flike all baby anteaters, prefers the
OL,19,Fsafety of mum for now.
OL,26,@xD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1775139065
OL,3,CRare giant anteater pup born at zoo
OL,5,F"This means that for the next six to
OL,6,F12 months it will be riding round on
OL,7,Fits mother's back, which is such a
OL,8,Flovely sight to see.
OL,10,F"With such distinctive markings it is
OL,11,Fa little hard to spot the baby at
OL,12,Ffirst as it blends in with mum, but it
OL,13,Fis worth a closer look, as once you
OL,14,Fcatch a glimpse of that tiny snout,
OL,15,Fyou won't be able to take your eyes
OL,16,Foff it!"
OL,18,FThe birth represents a vital win for
OL,19,Fthe species as giant anteaters are
OL,20,Fcurrently classified as vulnerable to
OL,21,Fextinction in the wild.
OL,26,@rD@AOUxD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
